Knowledge Base

Back to Semrush
Impactful Analytics
for Content
Marketing Heroes
ImpactHero is an AI tool that breaks down your content by buyer journey stages, detects the most impactful copy, and gives tips on reinforcing your efforts.
Sign up for a free trial
No credit card required. It means that you will not be automatically charged at the end of the trial period.
Your Personal Customer
Journey Analyst
Using a special tracking code, the tool scans the entire content
of your site and provides AI-driven recommendations on improving your content strategy, stage by stage.
Identify Your Content
Power Zones and Strengthen Your Business
Assess your content funnel.
Find high-performing content and tailor it to customer stages.
Analyze content with AI.
Get AI-generated content marketing improvements to deliver business results.
Look at the big picture of your
content marketing efforts.
See where your users are dropping off
and improve the weak spots.
Make your team focus on
what is best for your business.
The tool is designed for marketers and contains only the data they really need. Analyze data faster and a lot more easily.
Discover the impact
of your content
Sign up for a free trial
No credit card required. It means that you will not be automatically charged at the end of the trial period.
Take Full Control of Your Content
with Smart Features
Customer journey mapping
Visualize user flow to see the whole picture of your funnel performance.
Performance by content type and length
Find the most powerful content types on each stage of your marketing funnel.
Traffic sources
Analyze the customer journey by traffic sources to find your top-performing channels.
Data-driven insights
Our AI algorithms identify the areas for improvement and highlight them directly in the tool interface.
How it works
Step 1
Enter your domain.


Step 2
Install the code using

Step 3
Allow some time
for data collection.
Step 4
Explore the insights
we provide.
Powered by
Leading suite
for Marketing
8,000,000+
users have already tried Semrush
Since 2008
Inspiring marketers
“I’ve appreciated the regular insights, performance updates,
and variety of tools available in the ImpactHero tool.
It is very helpful to see the importance of a page from a conversion standpoint alongside its ability to engage customers all the way through to its final sentence.

Our marketing team is looking forward to seeing this tool
evolve over time to incorporate it into our SEO strategy and keep improving our content!”
Savannah Paver
SEO & Web Content Strategist for M/I Homes, Inc.
“Content plays a critical role in our marketing strategy, and ImpactHero helps us measure results and pivot to ensure we’re accomplishing what we’ve set out to do – engage and convert website visitors. We can now see the complete content user journey and identify new ways to convert website visitors.

ImpactHero shows us both the big picture of overall content performance and the details of how visitors interact with specific pieces, which helps us fine-tune our content strategy.”
Debra B. McCraw
Director, Content Marketing Strategy, for CompTIA
